# PrismX Roadmap (v0.1.28 → v1.2.0+)

---

## PHASE 1: Foundation & Core Features

### v0.1.28 — Mindmap & Workspace Enhancements

* Double-click editing
* Right-click menus
* View switcher (radial/tree/timeline)

### v0.1.29 — Triage & Inbox Redesign

* Priority sorting
* Tag assignments
* Shard-to-kanban logic

### v0.1.30 — Zen Mode & Breathing UI

* Breathing visual overlay
* Zen scratchpad autosave
* Zen-on-startup option

### v0.1.31 — Keybinding & Shortcut UX

* Command overlay (Ctrl+?)
* Multi-key support (e.g. Ctrl+K, T)
* Keymap override config

### v0.1.32 — Plugin Host Expansion

* Capability manifest v2
* Async hooks (on\_start, on\_tick)
* TUI slot rendering

### v0.1.33 — Dashboard Layout Engine

* Widget grid config (dashboard\_config.json)
* Slot render API
* Dashboard themes

### v0.1.34 — Smart Templating System

* YAML/JSON task/project templates
* Scheduled routine spawn
* Template API for extensions

### v0.1.35 — Encryption & Hidden Shards

* Shard encryption
* Toggle visibility
* Unlock via CLI or biometric

### v0.1.36 — RoutineForge Extension

* Morning/weekly routine builder
* Ad-hoc override days
* Visual scheduler interface

### v0.1.37 — Developer Diagnostics View

* Plugin profiling
* Capability audit
* Memory usage monitor

### v0.1.38 — Polish & Migration Engine

* Config/data versioning
* Lint cleanup
* CI checks for JSON schema

---

## PHASE 2: Architecture & Power Layer

### v0.2.0 — Unified Capability Router

* Centralized PrismCapability enforcement
* All system modules go through same gate

### v0.2.1 — Offline-First Enforcement Mode

* offline\_mode = true disables all network, AI, plugin IO
* Secure sandbox fallback

### v0.2.2 — Virtualized Shard Model

* NodeGroup abstraction for Shard/Workspace/Project
* Metadata support

### v0.2.3 — Object Metadata & Smart Filters

* Arbitrary "meta" fields per object
* Used in plugin filters and search queries

### v0.2.4 — Reactive Signal Bus

* emit(Signal::...) pattern for system triggers
* Extension & TUI event subscriptions

### v0.2.5 — Embedded Scripting (Rhai)

* Scripted extensions, workflows, macros
* Reactive hooks: on\_save, on\_start

### v0.2.6 — Dynamic Layout Profiles

* Switchable dashboard/workspace TUI layouts
* Time/context-sensitive view rules

### v0.2.7 — Declarative UI Configs

* keymaps.json, widgets.json, themes.json
* Live-reload interface logic

---

## PHASE 3: Infrastructure-Scale Integrations

### v1.0.0 — Public Stable Release

* GitHub Actions CI/CD
* Signed binaries
* Public plugin showcase

### v1.1.0 — Extension Registry

* `prismx plugin install name`
* Manifest + trust filter validation

### v1.1.1 — Secure Plugin Sandboxing

* Memory/time caps for each execution
* Audit trail of access

### v1.1.2 — Offline Docs Browser

* Fuzzy searchable help overlay
* Auto-index plugin docs + commands

### v1.1.3 — Multi-Shard Overlay Mode

* Render multiple shards simultaneously
* Border-styled TUI overlay rendering

### v1.1.4 — Biometric Shortcut Support

* TouchID, FaceID, Yubikey unlocks
* Trigger plugin or shard access events

### v1.1.5 — Audit Logging System

* Log user/plugin actions and errors
* Stored as `.audit/*.jsonl`

### v1.1.6 — Theming & Typography Engine

* High contrast, font-size, padding controls
* User-customizable `theme.json`

### v1.1.7 — Deferred Execution Queue

* "Run plugin later" or "after idle"
* Background automation queues

---

## Beyond v1.2.x

* Live Collaboration Engine
* AI Bridge (modular opt-in with capabilities)
* Git/USB Sync Engine
* Graph Analytics Views
* GUI Frontend Wrapper (optional)
